OL,3,CCouple who died after crash 'could
OL,4,Chave been distracted' by police
OL,6,FAn inquest has heard how a couple who
OL,7,Fdied after a crash near Appleby could
OL,8,Fhave been distracted by police who
OL,9,Ffollowed them.
OL,11,FRyan Duffy, 24, and Ellie Marsden, 20,
OL,12,Fboth from Wigan, were found dead
OL,13,Finside a van which had crashed off the
OL,14,Froad close to Kings Meaburn on the
OL,15,Fmorning of 5 September 2021.
OL,17,FThe couple had spent the evening in
OL,18,FAppleby, checking into a local hotel
OL,19,Fbefore spending two hours in the
OL,20,Ftown's Hare & Hounds pub.
