OL,6,FA jury was shown CCTV footage that
OL,7,Frecorded Ryan and Ellie's return to
OL,8,Ftheir van after midnight and the
OL,9,Fmoment they drove away.
OL,11,FIn this recording, a Cumbria Police
OL,12,Fvehicle begins to follow the van from
OL,13,FAppleby town centre.
OL,15,FA separate CCTV recording taken from a
OL,16,Fservice station close to the hamlet of
OL,17,FBurrells shows the police vehicle
OL,18,Fcontinuing to follow the van to an
OL,19,Farea close to the site where the van
OL,20,Fwas later found to have crashed.
