OL,6,FPS Wakefield said that the most likely
OL,7,Fcause of the crash was late steering
OL,8,Fthat was inappropriate to the speed of
OL,9,Fthe van due to distraction or
OL,10,Fintoxication.
OL,12,FPC Stevensen told a lawyer for Ryan
OL,13,FDuffy's family that an awareness of
OL,14,Fhim following them could have been a
OL,15,Fsignificant distraction.
OL,17,FThe inquest heard how the officer had
OL,18,Fstopped following the van 170 yards
OL,19,Ffrom where the vehicle crashed.
